whiteled government antiapartheid demonstrations are expected 
while de klerk is in washington 
de klerk also is scheduled to seek us support for proposals 
for an 11nation southern african economic confederation south 
africa which has the most powerful economy in the region believes 
it can help improve conditions in neighboring nations 
